{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/hcm-05222023090034.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-05-22T11:18:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-05-22T13:05:16-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "G7\u53d1\u5e03\u8054\u5408\u516c\u62a5\u3000\u805a\u7126\u4e2d\u56fd\u7ecf\u6d4e\u80c1\u8feb", "description": "\u4e03\u5927\u5de5\u4e1a\u56fd\u96c6\u56e2\u9ad8\u5cf0\u4f1a\u65e5\u524d\u53d1\u8868\u8054\u5408\u58f0\u660e\u5f3a\u8c03\uff0c\u6210\u5458\u56fd\u5fc5\u987b\u62b5\u5fa1\u4e2d\u56fd\u7684\u7ecf\u6d4e\u80c1\u8feb\u3002\u7f8e\u56fd\u603b\u7edf\u62dc\u767b\u5728\u8bb0\u8005\u4f1a\u4e0a\u4e5f\u8868\u793a\uff0c\u6210\u5458\u56fd\u5bf9\u4e8e\u4e2d\u56fd\u5df2\u8fbe\u6210\u4e00\u81f4\u770b\u6cd5\u3002", "videos": [], "audios": ["https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/hcm-05222023090034.html/@@stream"], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/hcm-05222023090034.html/@@images/3f2fc69e-5576-4258-992d-5a4a523f9e17.jpeg\"/>\n\u53f0\u6e7e\u7684\u56fd\u7b56\u9662\u4e3e\u884c\u201cGT\u3001\u7f8e\u65e5\u97e9\u5cf0\u4f1a\u4e0e\u7f8e\u4e2d\u6218\u7565\u5bf9\u6297\u201d\u5ea7\u8c08\u4f1a\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/hcm-05222023090034.html/@@images/image\">\n</a>\n\u8bb0\u8005 \u9ec4\u6625\u6885\u6444\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"G7\\u53d1\\u5e03\\u8054\\u5408\\u516c\\u62a5\\u3000\\u805a\\u7126\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u7ecf\\u6d4e\\u80c1\\u8feb\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n                    \"article_uid\": utag_data[\"article_uid\"],\n                    \"media_type\": \"onDemand audio\",\n                    